              </p>
              <img class="is-absolute is-hidden-mobile is-top-0 is-right-0 mt-8 image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-3-widescreen is-6-tablet pt-0 step-card">
            <div class="mx-auto has-text-centered is-relative">
              <div class="mb-4 pb-4 is-inline-flex is-align-items-center is-justify-content-center is-relative">
                <div class="number-circle-container">
                  <div class="is-absolute is-top-0 is-left-0 number-circle step-2">
                    <h2 class="has-text-weight-bold number-step m-auto">2</h2>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <%= image_tag "main/step-2" %>
              </div>
              <h2 class="title is-spaced step-title p-0 mb-3">We review your application</h2>
              <p class="subtitle step-subtitle">
                Your application will be evaluated by our board members for a multi-perspective score.
                If approved, your rescue will become an accredited partner of ERA.
              </p>
              <img class="is-absolute is-hidden-touch is-hidden-desktop-only is-top-0 is-right-0 mt-8 image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-3-widescreen is-6-tablet pt-0 step-card">
            <div class="mx-auto has-text-centered is-relative">
              <div class="mb-4 pb-4 is-inline-flex is-align-items-center is-justify-content-center is-relative">
                <div class="number-circle-container">
                  <div class="is-absolute is-top-0 is-left-0 number-circle step-3">
                    <h2 class="has-text-weight-bold number-step m-auto">3</h2>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <%= image_tag "main/step-3" %>
              </div>
              <h2 class="title is-spaced step-title p-0 mb-3">Benefits begin immediately</h2>
              <p class="subtitle step-subtitle">
                After approval, ERA will provide areas of support such as product resources,
                access to mentorships, and the ability to connect with other accredited rescues.
              </p>
              <img class="is-absolute is-hidden-mobile is-top-0 is-right-0 mt-8 image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-3-widescreen is-6-tablet pt-0 step-card">
            <div class="mx-auto has-text-centered">
              <div class="mb-4 pb-4 is-inline-flex is-align-items-center is-justify-content-center is-relative">
                <div class="number-circle-container">
                  <div class="is-absolute is-top-0 is-left-0 number-circle step-4">
                    <h2 class="has-text-weight-bold number-step m-auto">4</h2>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <%= image_tag "main/step-4" %>
              </div>
              <h2 class="title is-spaced step-title p-0 mb-3">Maintain your accreditation</h2>
              <p class="subtitle step-subtitle">
                By upholding the Code of Ethics, your rescue will continue to be
                recognized as an accredited partner of ERA. We will continue to support you along the way.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="testimonial-hero is-small testimonial-container mb-6">
      <div class="hero-body">
        <div class="b-testimonial-rotate mt-3">
          <div class="item">
            <em>
              As an ethical breeder with a deep history in rescue, I support the Ethical Rescue Association's mission to establish ethical guidelines for grass roots reform.
            </em>
            <br>
            <b class="is-size-7">— Nikki L. —</b>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <em>
              An Ethical Rescue Association is needed to prevent the peddling of dangerous animals to the public by rescues with a savior complex.
            </em>
            <br>
            <b class="is-size-7">— Katie W. —</b>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <em>
              This movement is crucial in preventing dogs from having long term stays in a shelter, and then being placed in an unfit home.
            </em>
            <br><b class="is-size-7">— Lydia L. —</b>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <em>
              Finding an ethical rescue can be extremely difficult, especially if you're inexperienced. A group like ERA has been needed for a very long time.
            </em>
            <br><b class="is-size-7">— Jessica C. —</b>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <em>
              There is absolutely a need for an organization like this.  Too often rescues are formed and there's no one to ensure they are doing as they should.
            </em>
            <br><b class="is-size-7">— Ruth B. —</b>
          </div>
          <div class="dots"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<%= render 'payment_prompt' %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "main_script" %>

<script>
  function bTestimonial() {
  let instance = document.querySelectorAll('.b-testimonial-rotate');
  instance.forEach(function(item) {
    initCar(item)
  })

  function initCar(el) {
    let items = el.querySelectorAll('.item')
    let dots = el.querySelector('.dots')
    let slides = items.length

    //Create dots
    items.forEach(function(el) {
      let dot = document.createElement('div')
      dot.classList.add('dot')
      dots.appendChild(dot)
    })

    //Play the carousel
    function playCar( items, dotsNode ) {
      let dots = Array.from(dotsNode.querySelectorAll('.dot'))
      let i = 1
      items[0].classList.add('is-active', 'init');
      dots[0].classList.add('is-active');
      setInterval(function() {
          items.forEach(function(el) {
            el.classList.remove('is-active')
          })
          dots.forEach(function(el) {el.classList.remove('is-active') })
          if ( i < (items.length - 1) ) {
            let item = items[i]
            let dot = dots[i]
            item.classList.add('is-active', 'init');
            dot.classList.add('is-active');
            i++
          } else {
            items[i].classList.add('is-active', 'init');
            dots[i].classList.add('is-active');
            i = 0
          }
      }, 6000)
    }

    playCar(items, dots)

  }
}

document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', bTestimonial() )

</script>